&lt;h1 id="you-werent-meant-to-have-a-boss"&gt;You Weren&amp;rsquo;t Meant to Have a Boss&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Want to start a startup? Get funded by Y Combinator.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;March 2008, rev. June 2008&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Technology tends to separate normal from natural. Our bodies weren&amp;rsquo;t designed to eat the foods that people in rich countries eat, or to get so little exercise. There may be a similar problem with the way we work: a normal job may be as bad for us intellectually as white flour or sugar is for us physically.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>